If you would like to delete your Harrier account and associated data, please send an email to:

admin@harrier.land

Subject:
Delete My Account

Please send the request from the email address associated with your Harrier account.

## What data will be deleted

When your deletion request is processed, the following data will be permanently removed:

- User account information
- Profile information
- User-generated content associated with the account
- App usage data linked to the account

## Data that may be retained

Some information may be retained for a limited period where required for:

- Legal obligations
- Security investigations
- Fraud prevention
- Backup and recovery processes

Any retained information will be deleted when no longer required.

## Processing time

Deletion requests are typically processed within 30 days.
